WEBVTT

01:39.490 --> 01:43.600
[Road to Success]

01:44.640 --> 01:47.770
[Episode 3]

01:48.920 --> 01:49.560
How did you defend it?

01:49.560 --> 01:51.820
-How are you holding up?
-Where were you?

01:52.920 --> 01:53.509
Here.

01:53.509 --> 01:54.509
Have some water.

01:59.840 --> 02:00.480
Here.

02:01.760 --> 02:02.820
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

02:15.150 --> 02:16.360
Good job, everyone.

02:16.760 --> 02:17.690
Do you want to

02:17.710 --> 02:19.380
share your thoughts?

02:26.970 --> 02:28.040
I'll go first.

02:28.650 --> 02:31.430
-Idiot referee!
-Wait! Are you out of your mind?

02:31.930 --> 02:32.930
You missed your chance.

02:32.930 --> 02:33.610
Next.

02:44.710 --> 02:45.630
I really didn't realize

02:45.630 --> 02:46.890
my hand had touched the ball.

02:46.890 --> 02:48.610
You didn't touch it at all.

02:48.680 --> 02:50.150
That referee is blind.

02:50.150 --> 02:52.160
It was a borderline call.

02:52.190 --> 02:53.590
Why give them a penalty?

02:54.150 --> 02:55.710
Forget it.

02:55.710 --> 02:57.940
They always call it against
small teams like us.

02:57.940 --> 02:59.260
I told you.

02:59.290 --> 03:01.780
We shouldn't have come here
just to get humiliated.

03:01.780 --> 03:02.680
Ms. Lin,

03:03.030 --> 03:04.750
who is this guy next to you?

03:09.010 --> 03:10.470
I forgot to introduce him.

03:10.680 --> 03:12.360
He's my primary school classmate

03:12.360 --> 03:14.110
who just came back from abroad.

03:14.150 --> 03:15.280
He's a professional football coach.

03:15.280 --> 03:17.430
Make your lies somewhat logical.

03:17.710 --> 03:20.910
Do you know how hard it is
to get a coaching license abroad?

03:20.960 --> 03:23.090
Miss, he's trying to hit on you, right?

03:23.750 --> 03:26.030
Don't call him out.

03:29.240 --> 03:29.680
Yes.

03:30.470 --> 03:33.329
-He's not even pretending anymore.
-What did I say?

03:34.870 --> 03:35.960
I mean

03:35.960 --> 03:38.030
getting a football coaching license abroad

03:38.030 --> 03:39.230
is indeed difficult.

03:44.240 --> 03:46.430
Why would a professional football coach

03:46.430 --> 03:47.310
who just came back from abroad

03:47.310 --> 03:48.690
come to watch our school football game?

03:48.690 --> 03:49.720
Don't you find it boring?

03:49.720 --> 03:50.510
Yeah.

03:50.690 --> 03:51.370
Not at all.

03:52.510 --> 03:54.120
I think every football match

03:54.560 --> 03:55.760
is very interesting.

03:58.870 --> 04:00.070
Any other questions?

04:01.030 --> 04:02.310
If you are a coach,

04:02.310 --> 04:04.310
are you the kind who coaches kids?

04:07.240 --> 04:08.810
I used to coach a youth team.

04:09.030 --> 04:10.430
Now I'm unemployed.

04:10.430 --> 04:11.400
Youth team?

04:11.400 --> 04:12.750
Which lousy club?

04:18.920 --> 04:19.760
Nanton.

04:27.840 --> 04:29.130
Impossible.

04:29.600 --> 04:30.630
Do you know

04:30.630 --> 04:32.600
where Nanton Youth Team stands in Europe?

04:32.600 --> 04:33.200
Well then,

04:33.560 --> 04:34.430
tell me.

04:34.430 --> 04:36.120
Last year in the European Youth League,

04:36.120 --> 04:37.920
how many points did Nanton get

04:37.920 --> 04:38.800
in the first stage of the first season?

04:38.800 --> 04:40.130
What was their ranking?

04:44.870 --> 04:45.720
Do you know?

04:45.870 --> 04:46.909
Can't I test him?

04:50.830 --> 04:51.600
First place.

04:52.270 --> 04:53.040
First stage,

04:53.510 --> 04:54.190
8 matches,

04:54.480 --> 04:55.310
20 points.

04:57.600 --> 05:01.000
Then who did they play in the last match
and what was the score?

05:05.120 --> 05:06.430
If you're so good,

05:06.430 --> 05:07.630
why did you come back?

05:14.390 --> 05:15.160
I don't mind

05:15.160 --> 05:17.190
telling you stories
for the whole second half.

05:17.190 --> 05:18.430
But my primary school classmate

05:18.430 --> 05:19.360
might mind.

05:20.040 --> 05:20.860
That's right.

05:21.070 --> 05:22.000
I asked him here

05:22.000 --> 05:24.040
to teach you guys

05:24.040 --> 05:25.760
some football tactics for the second half.

05:25.760 --> 05:27.310
Isn't this just a formality?

05:27.310 --> 05:28.310
Do we really need tactics?

05:28.310 --> 05:29.000
Right.

05:34.750 --> 05:36.190
Our problem right now is,

05:36.730 --> 05:38.360
firstly, our stamina may not hold up.

05:38.360 --> 05:39.409
Secondly,

05:39.430 --> 05:40.490
our morale is low,

05:40.580 --> 05:42.130
and their attack is really strong.

05:42.130 --> 05:44.360
We probably won't be able to
hold them off in the second half.

05:44.360 --> 05:45.960
Do you have any suggestions?

05:49.430 --> 05:50.830
Your opponent, Ning'an,

05:51.490 --> 05:52.930
is nicknamed the Cheetah.

05:52.930 --> 05:54.060
As the name implies,

05:54.159 --> 05:54.990
they are fast,

05:55.120 --> 05:55.920
but they also have a weakness.

05:55.920 --> 05:57.040
Who doesn't know that?

05:57.040 --> 05:58.040
They have weak endurance.

05:58.040 --> 05:58.830
Right.

05:59.070 --> 06:00.930
But your endurance is even worse.

06:01.090 --> 06:03.690
You guys haven't trained
in a long time, right?

06:05.390 --> 06:06.360
Qin Ao.

06:07.050 --> 06:08.110
Any suggestions?

06:08.600 --> 06:09.680
If you want to win,

06:10.240 --> 06:11.240
just listen to me.

06:14.600 --> 06:17.950
It feels like
he's speaking in professional terms.

06:18.590 --> 06:20.520
But when he puts them all together,

06:21.160 --> 06:22.690
I can't understand a thing.

06:30.740 --> 06:31.750
This guy

06:32.270 --> 06:33.630
is really weird.

06:35.159 --> 06:37.409
Why did he suddenly appear at my house,

06:37.440 --> 06:39.170
and then suddenly appear here?

06:40.500 --> 06:41.670
Is it really

06:42.390 --> 06:43.950
just a coincidence?

06:48.750 --> 06:49.659
Never mind.

06:50.000 --> 06:51.659
I'll focus on the match first.

06:54.550 --> 06:56.150
Those who want to hear the tactics,

06:56.150 --> 06:56.780
come here.

06:56.800 --> 06:57.800
Lin Lu, hurry.

06:57.830 --> 06:58.600
-Come here, everyone.
-Let's just listen.

06:58.600 --> 07:00.070
There's no harm anyway.

07:00.070 --> 07:00.680
Let's go.

07:02.750 --> 07:03.730
Fu.

07:06.940 --> 07:09.070
Come on, defenders, raise your hands.

07:10.870 --> 07:12.330
You three start from here.

07:12.830 --> 07:13.970
Although the curling shots...

07:13.970 --> 07:15.200
I'm so sleepy.

07:15.270 --> 07:16.120
Are a bit hard for you now.

07:16.120 --> 07:18.510
I hope this QR Code is reliable

07:18.830 --> 07:20.510
and can actually be useful.

07:22.420 --> 07:23.370
Of course.

07:23.800 --> 07:26.070
If the forwards are making a run
in the same direction,

07:26.070 --> 07:27.270
a driven pass will do.

07:28.920 --> 07:29.920
That simple?

07:30.910 --> 07:33.170
Wouldn't that be easy to defend against?

07:33.600 --> 07:34.480
In football,

07:34.950 --> 07:36.750
there are many complex tactics,

07:37.290 --> 07:38.570
but there is only one

07:38.640 --> 07:39.840
that is the simplest.

07:40.240 --> 07:41.240
Which one?

07:43.320 --> 07:44.560
Always stay focused.

07:45.930 --> 07:47.000
Your focus should always

07:47.000 --> 07:47.870
be on the ball.

07:49.190 --> 07:51.750
Elevating tactics
to a philosophical level—

07:52.510 --> 07:54.170
he sure can talk.

07:54.200 --> 07:55.240
Ms. Lin,

07:55.260 --> 07:56.920
be careful not to get tricked.

07:57.480 --> 07:59.270
I'm also worried.

08:00.860 --> 08:02.460
You're going to lose anyway.

08:03.290 --> 08:04.420
Why not give it a try?

08:08.390 --> 08:09.600
That makes sense.

08:10.160 --> 08:11.750
We're here to have fun anyway.

08:11.750 --> 08:12.720
Just be happy.

08:14.200 --> 08:14.950
Come on!

08:14.260 --> 08:16.830
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

08:14.950 --> 08:16.490
-Come on!
-Come on!

08:16.490 --> 08:18.410
-Come on!
-Come on!

08:16.860 --> 08:20.550
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

08:24.310 --> 08:25.660
Do you want to try

08:26.190 --> 08:26.920
that method?

08:28.010 --> 08:29.270
What are you thinking?

08:29.590 --> 08:31.040
It's impossible for a Chinese person

08:31.040 --> 08:33.130
to coach a European football club.

08:34.750 --> 08:36.110
If what he said is true,

08:36.130 --> 08:38.789
I could play
in one of Europe's top five leagues.

08:39.440 --> 08:40.630
He's a fraud.

08:45.600 --> 08:46.840
The second half begins.

08:46.840 --> 08:48.320
The teams switch sides.

08:48.320 --> 08:50.480
Ning'an Experimental School
is still in the lead.

08:50.480 --> 08:51.600
2-0.

08:51.710 --> 08:53.550
Ning'an Experimental School still

08:53.550 --> 08:55.550
still leads 2-0.

08:55.550 --> 08:57.240
Hongjing No. 8 High School's attack

08:57.240 --> 08:58.510
is intercepted again.

08:58.510 --> 08:59.670
Counterattack!

09:00.790 --> 09:02.630
Ning'an Experimental School
breaks into the penalty area—

09:02.630 --> 09:03.720
a shot from a tight angle!

09:03.720 --> 09:04.630
Feng Suo!

09:04.870 --> 09:06.910
He saved the ball!

09:07.270 --> 09:09.470
They all say your method is unreliable.

09:10.030 --> 09:10.960
Will it work?

09:11.960 --> 09:12.750
Indeed.

09:13.390 --> 09:14.270
A normal coach

09:14.270 --> 09:15.800
wouldn't set it up this way.

09:15.950 --> 09:17.280
But I'm no normal coach.

09:19.440 --> 09:21.910
How would
a normal coach set it up then?

09:21.910 --> 09:24.240
They would have them
play mid-block defense first,

09:24.240 --> 09:25.440
draw the opponent's attack,

09:25.440 --> 09:27.300
and then launch a counterattack.

09:34.170 --> 09:35.560
Then why didn't you?

09:37.000 --> 09:38.660
We're already behind anyway.

09:38.950 --> 09:40.410
We might as well go all out.

09:41.960 --> 09:42.790
More importantly,

09:42.790 --> 09:44.650
I can't let your money go to waste.

09:46.080 --> 09:47.410
After all, I'm worth it.

09:56.660 --> 09:58.580
Boss, I really can't run anymore.

09:58.600 --> 10:00.350
I feel like I'll drop dead
if I keep running.

10:00.350 --> 10:01.180
Slow down. Don't get hurt.

10:01.180 --> 10:01.910
Take it easy.

10:02.030 --> 10:02.560
Alright.

10:05.870 --> 10:08.460
Why is the opponent obviously exhausted

10:08.480 --> 10:09.880
but still trying so hard?

10:09.930 --> 10:11.330
Because you are too weak,

10:11.720 --> 10:13.580
and they want to score more goals.

10:14.360 --> 10:15.600
So cunning.

10:17.240 --> 10:18.360
The goalkeeper
of Hongjing No. 8 High School

10:18.360 --> 10:20.150
throws the ball to No. 6 Lin Lu.

10:20.150 --> 10:22.810
Lin Lu passes to No. 10 Fu Xinshu.

10:23.510 --> 10:25.270
Try a long pass from the backfield

10:25.270 --> 10:26.400
to find the forward.

10:26.440 --> 10:29.100
Just rely on the forward's
precise first touch.

10:33.430 --> 10:35.070
Qin Ao, Chen Jianghe!

10:35.120 --> 10:36.270
-Let's try it.
-A long pass!

10:36.270 --> 10:37.910
It's actually a long pass tactic!

10:37.910 --> 10:39.720
The pass goes over
Ning'an Experimental School's defense line

10:39.720 --> 10:41.000
and reaches the forward!

10:41.000 --> 10:41.720
Qin Ao!

10:42.270 --> 10:43.080
They're very fast!

10:43.080 --> 10:44.440
This ball is passed to Chen Jianghe!

10:44.440 --> 10:45.670
Chen Jianghe shoots!

10:45.670 --> 10:47.480
What a pity. The shot is blocked.

10:47.480 --> 10:48.150
Although it didn't go in,

10:48.150 --> 10:49.440
this is the first time

10:49.440 --> 10:50.720
we've seen effective teamwork from

10:50.720 --> 10:54.030
-Hongjing No. 8 High School, come on!
-Hongjing No. 8 High School! What happened just now?

10:54.030 --> 10:54.790
Their form

10:54.790 --> 10:56.360
has obviously improved.

10:56.360 --> 10:58.030
It's impossible
for a Chinese person to coach

10:58.030 --> 11:00.320
a European football club.

11:00.350 --> 11:00.980
Wide.

11:02.120 --> 11:03.550
If what he said is true,

11:03.550 --> 11:04.840
I could play
in one of Europe's top five leagues.

11:04.840 --> 11:05.990
Too high.

11:06.750 --> 11:07.390
It's over.

11:08.320 --> 11:09.200
It's a mess.

11:10.550 --> 11:11.840
Can you stop talking?

11:20.670 --> 11:22.860
[78']

11:23.080 --> 11:25.240
It's the 78th minute of the match.

11:25.240 --> 11:26.910
Hongjing No. 8 High School
has a corner kick,

11:26.910 --> 11:28.830
taken by No. 6, Lin Lu.

11:37.150 --> 11:39.000
The ball is passed to No. 9, Qin Ao.

11:39.000 --> 11:40.840
Qin Ao fails to win the header.

11:40.840 --> 11:42.670
Hongjing No. 8 High School

11:42.670 --> 11:44.120
no longer has the advantage in the air.

11:44.120 --> 11:46.920
Possession goes to
Ning'an Experimental School.

11:47.630 --> 11:49.240
No. 14 and No. 13

11:48.990 --> 11:49.510
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

11:49.240 --> 11:50.440
are linking up.

11:49.540 --> 11:50.000
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

11:50.440 --> 11:51.390
And shoot!

11:51.510 --> 11:54.910
The ball is saved by
Hongjing No. 8 High School's goalkeeper.

11:59.280 --> 12:02.030
Their players
are better built than our forwards.

12:02.030 --> 12:03.550
So normally,

12:03.900 --> 12:05.060
when you fight for the ball,

12:05.060 --> 12:06.320
you have no advantage.

12:09.400 --> 12:11.460
You need to be flexible
and avoid direct confrontation.

12:11.460 --> 12:14.130
Don't rely on your height in aerial duels.

12:14.160 --> 12:15.670
Keep your eyes on the landing point

12:15.670 --> 12:17.530
and compete for the second ball.

12:18.030 --> 12:19.600
We can see Qin Ao
from Hongjing No. 8 High School

12:19.600 --> 12:21.870
no longer going for aerial duels
like before,

12:21.870 --> 12:23.000
but instead moving to the landing point
to compete for the second ball.

12:23.000 --> 12:24.030
Let's trust him for now!

12:24.030 --> 12:25.270
It's a brilliant decision!

12:25.270 --> 12:26.670
He successfully intercepts the ball.

12:26.670 --> 12:28.480
How did Hongjing No. 8 High School
suddenly come up with this?

12:28.480 --> 12:30.680
Their new tactic is really impressive!

12:42.750 --> 12:43.870
It's a goal!

12:43.870 --> 12:46.320
-Well done!
-Congratulations to Hongjing No. 8 High School for pulling one back!

12:46.320 --> 12:48.360
The score is now 2-1.

12:56.730 --> 12:58.010
[Ning'an Experimental School 2–0
Hongjing No. 8 High School]

12:59.030 --> 13:00.000
Qin Ao!

13:00.000 --> 13:01.260
Nice shot!

13:01.280 --> 13:02.550
Nice shot!

13:03.320 --> 13:03.990
Bro!

13:04.250 --> 13:06.910
-The match is almost over.
-Well done!

13:06.910 --> 13:09.510
-One more!
-Let's go! One more goal!

13:09.510 --> 13:11.510
Such a goal is impossible to replicate.

13:11.510 --> 13:13.550
It not only helps them pull one back,

13:13.550 --> 13:14.750
but more importantly,

13:14.750 --> 13:16.200
it helps the whole team

13:16.200 --> 13:17.400
regain confidence.

13:18.030 --> 13:19.760
Keep trying to win possession.

13:19.960 --> 13:21.890
Play long balls up to the forwards.

13:21.960 --> 13:23.600
This QR Code

13:23.600 --> 13:25.080
really knows his stuff.

13:28.310 --> 13:29.360
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

13:28.600 --> 13:30.600
Three minutes of stoppage time
in the second half.

13:29.380 --> 13:30.480
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

13:30.600 --> 13:32.150
The current score is 2-1.

13:32.150 --> 13:33.750
Ning'an Experimental School
is in the lead.

13:33.750 --> 13:36.320
Players from both sides
are giving it their all.

13:36.320 --> 13:37.270
In the final moments,

13:37.270 --> 13:39.550
will Hongjing No. 8 High School equalize,

13:39.550 --> 13:41.720
or will Ning'an Experimental School
win the game?

13:41.720 --> 13:42.510
Fu!

13:43.000 --> 13:44.670
Ning'an Experimental School's corner kick—

13:44.670 --> 13:47.360
let's see who wins the second ball.

13:50.120 --> 13:51.270
No. 12, Chen Weidong,

13:51.270 --> 13:53.080
intercepted the ball.

13:53.200 --> 13:55.840
He might be offside!

13:56.200 --> 13:56.790
All their players

13:56.790 --> 13:58.360
are too close to our half.

13:58.360 --> 13:59.030
This forces our forwards

13:59.030 --> 14:00.400
to move back with them.

14:00.750 --> 14:01.790
It's easy to fall into an offside trap.

14:01.790 --> 14:03.200
Our space is too small.

14:05.910 --> 14:07.380
They are setting an offside trap.

14:07.380 --> 14:09.180
Can't you beat the offside trap?

14:12.030 --> 14:13.600
Because of your frequent attacks,

14:13.600 --> 14:15.370
their defenders are reaching their limit.

14:15.370 --> 14:16.710
Especially the right-back.

14:16.710 --> 14:18.540
He's slow to turn to his left.

14:18.570 --> 14:19.790
Play down his left side.

14:19.790 --> 14:20.990
Fall back and defend!

14:21.030 --> 14:22.360
They beat the offside trap!

14:22.360 --> 14:23.750
What an amazing decision!

14:23.750 --> 14:25.840
Would their defenders make such a mistake?

14:25.840 --> 14:27.600
They completely changed!

14:27.600 --> 14:30.260
They're showing
why they were once runners-up!

14:32.050 --> 14:33.720
If you are lucky enough.

14:41.360 --> 14:42.600
A goal!

14:42.600 --> 14:44.750
My God! In stoppage time!

14:44.750 --> 14:46.600
We didn't lose!

14:46.870 --> 14:48.870
It's a last-minute equalizer
to make it 2–2!

14:48.870 --> 14:49.720
Bravo!

14:49.750 --> 14:51.240
We didn't lose!

14:55.510 --> 14:57.150
Good shot!

14:57.170 --> 15:00.230
♪ Who isn't going through nights
of darkness and confusion ♪

15:01.010 --> 15:04.610
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

15:05.020 --> 15:11.020
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

15:09.080 --> 15:10.030
Thank you

15:10.030 --> 15:11.760
for helping them turn the tide.

15:12.480 --> 15:13.110
No need.

15:13.300 --> 15:15.970
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

15:13.750 --> 15:14.630
You paid for it.

15:16.040 --> 15:17.790
I can see

15:16.840 --> 15:20.410
♪ Looking up,
dreaming side by side of great ideals ♪

15:18.080 --> 15:20.030
that they didn't really want to lose.

15:20.030 --> 15:21.380
They were just afraid of losing face.

15:21.140 --> 15:26.930
♪ The vast world
awaits youth to arrive ♪

15:28.060 --> 15:30.760
♪ If braving the wind and waves ♪

15:31.640 --> 15:34.680
♪ Can be called growth ♪

15:35.050 --> 15:35.960
He just left?

15:35.740 --> 15:38.280
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

15:39.280 --> 15:41.950
♪ And run wild once ♪

15:39.620 --> 15:41.070
How rude.

15:42.990 --> 15:46.020
♪ Even if the road ahead is long ♪

15:47.090 --> 15:48.990
If you don't try your best,

15:47.210 --> 15:49.490
♪ I will still be unstoppable ♪

15:49.630 --> 15:50.870
luck won't favor you.

15:51.310 --> 15:52.250
♪ Break through all confusion ♪

15:53.230 --> 15:54.400
♪ Chase my own light ♪

15:55.800 --> 15:57.970
♪ In the storm I grow resilient wings ♪

15:59.000 --> 16:02.370
♪ Even if no one is clapping ♪

16:02.670 --> 16:04.510
-You practiced in secret?
-Amazing, right?

16:02.910 --> 16:04.920
♪ I will still fight my way forward ♪

16:04.510 --> 16:05.150
Just that one shot.

16:05.150 --> 16:06.270
Awesome, bro.

16:06.270 --> 16:07.750
You've definitely been practicing
in secret.

16:07.750 --> 16:08.550
Awesome.

16:09.870 --> 16:10.930
What are you doing?

16:11.790 --> 16:14.250
You must be Ms. Lin
from the P.E. department.

16:14.790 --> 16:15.790
I'm Director Jin.

16:16.390 --> 16:18.000
The chemistry competition just ended.

16:18.000 --> 16:19.550
Their bus happens to be broken.

16:19.550 --> 16:21.270
They have to rush back
for a post-competition review.

16:21.270 --> 16:22.530
Let us borrow your bus.

16:22.840 --> 16:25.440
Director Jin,
this is our football team's car.

16:25.510 --> 16:27.750
If your car is broken,

16:27.750 --> 16:29.610
how about we squeeze in together?

16:29.940 --> 16:30.930
But...

16:31.080 --> 16:32.360
There are only so many seats.

16:32.360 --> 16:33.750
I'm afraid we won't fit.

16:34.270 --> 16:35.600
The academic teachers are still waiting

16:35.600 --> 16:36.440
at school.

16:37.270 --> 16:39.530
You guys on the team,
please do me a favor.

16:39.670 --> 16:40.270
Thank you.

16:41.320 --> 16:43.920
I'll have the bus come back
to pick you up later.

16:50.240 --> 16:52.280
Aren't we in a hurry too?

16:52.390 --> 16:54.510
Mr. Jin is the most biased teacher.

16:54.510 --> 16:56.550
We're all tired after the match too.

16:56.550 --> 16:57.960
He didn't even pretend to care.

16:57.960 --> 17:00.420
He kicked the ladder away
after climbing up.

17:01.030 --> 17:02.000
Ms. Lin,

17:02.750 --> 17:03.870
what should we do?

17:05.079 --> 17:06.270
I don't know.

17:06.750 --> 17:08.000
I'm new here too.

17:14.589 --> 17:15.589
How about

17:15.680 --> 17:17.069
I treat you to something nice to eat?

17:17.069 --> 17:17.750
Ms. Lin,

17:17.750 --> 17:20.440
I know a really good
stir-fry restaurant nearby.

17:20.440 --> 17:22.200
But... it's a bit expensive.

17:23.190 --> 17:24.300
It doesn't matter.

17:24.319 --> 17:25.660
As long as you're happy.

17:26.109 --> 17:26.660
Where is it?

17:26.660 --> 17:27.530
Over there.

17:28.410 --> 17:28.940
Let's go.

17:29.310 --> 17:30.510
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

18:00.930 --> 18:01.930
How did you get in?

18:03.070 --> 18:05.190
The door downstairs was wide open.

18:05.480 --> 18:07.210
And your own door was unlocked.

18:08.570 --> 18:10.020
Stop looking so miserable.

18:10.020 --> 18:11.350
Look what I brought you.

18:13.640 --> 18:15.110
Doesn't it make the place feel more alive?

18:15.110 --> 18:15.710
It's okay.

18:16.880 --> 18:18.070
Store them yourself.

18:18.070 --> 18:18.720
Just okay?

18:19.030 --> 18:20.890
How would you survive without me?

18:22.590 --> 18:25.550
Wi-Fi, Wi-Fi, Wi-Fi.

18:31.500 --> 18:32.100
Wang Fa.

18:32.670 --> 18:33.240
Why

18:33.240 --> 18:35.370
isn't the password
on the back of the router?

18:35.370 --> 18:36.770
The password is 8 eights.

18:37.000 --> 18:37.880
Internet isn't that expensive.

18:37.880 --> 18:39.140
Eight eights?

18:39.160 --> 18:40.070
Change it.

18:40.070 --> 18:41.550
That's too easy to guess.

18:41.550 --> 18:42.770
Anyone can connect.

18:42.800 --> 18:44.280
Alright, connected.

18:44.300 --> 18:47.210
Sharing the same network makes us family.

18:47.240 --> 18:48.720
Who's your family?

18:49.250 --> 18:50.780
Did my sister say yes to you?

18:51.880 --> 18:53.830
Watch your mouth.

18:53.830 --> 18:56.030
Once I, Yu Bo, am your agent,

18:56.030 --> 18:57.590
I'm your agent for life.

18:57.900 --> 18:59.450
Of course we're family.

19:02.030 --> 19:03.160
Your new house is...

19:04.070 --> 19:06.160
Who's calling at this hour?

19:09.070 --> 19:09.720
Hello?

19:10.260 --> 19:11.870
How did the interview go?

19:13.910 --> 19:14.970
Really?

19:15.350 --> 19:16.350
That's great.

19:16.350 --> 19:17.160
Yes.

19:17.160 --> 19:18.960
I also think I'm indeed

19:18.960 --> 19:21.310
the best fit for Yongchuan Hengjiu.

19:21.550 --> 19:22.070
Okay.

19:22.070 --> 19:22.790
I got it.

19:23.270 --> 19:23.720
Bye.

19:25.590 --> 19:26.160
I got it.

19:26.160 --> 19:27.830
Yes! Yes! Yes!

19:28.110 --> 19:29.830
My lifelong agent

19:29.830 --> 19:31.000
is running away now?

19:31.480 --> 19:34.160
I'm going to Yongchuan Hengjiu.

19:34.160 --> 19:37.880
Yongchuan
is the closest place to your sister.

19:42.240 --> 19:43.000
Let me borrow a suit of yours.

19:43.000 --> 19:44.850
I need to look the part.

19:56.580 --> 19:58.170
[Studied in the UK] [Psychology major]

19:58.190 --> 19:59.620
[Likes spicy food] [Hates coriander]

19:59.640 --> 20:00.760
[Not good at sports] [Can't ride a bike]
[Hates rainy days]

20:00.820 --> 20:09.510
[Spade Q, Lin Wanxing]

20:11.920 --> 20:13.850
Did you come all the way to Hongjing

20:14.810 --> 20:16.670
just to investigate Lin Wanxing?

20:16.830 --> 20:17.350
Yes.

20:20.350 --> 20:21.200
Lin Wanxing

20:22.320 --> 20:23.630
is my landlady now.

20:27.430 --> 20:28.690
She lives downstairs.

20:32.770 --> 20:33.490
Okay.

20:36.740 --> 20:38.110
-This hits the spot.
-7, 8, 9, 10, 11.

20:38.110 --> 20:40.160
Nothing like an iced tea after a match.

20:40.160 --> 20:41.550
If we hadn't run into Jin Laoyao today,

20:41.550 --> 20:43.010
it would've been perfect.

20:43.270 --> 20:45.270
It's not the first time
we've been despised.

20:45.270 --> 20:46.640
Aren't you used to it by now?

20:46.640 --> 20:47.510
True.

20:47.510 --> 20:48.960
A lousy football team

20:48.960 --> 20:49.820
means nothing.

20:50.680 --> 20:51.350
Guys,

20:51.350 --> 20:53.030
don't come to me
for this kind of thing again.

20:53.030 --> 20:54.390
It's too annoying.

20:54.420 --> 20:55.530
Don't say that.

20:55.790 --> 20:56.750
We got our special admission spots

20:56.750 --> 20:58.350
because we played football.

20:58.480 --> 20:59.000
Yeah.

20:59.440 --> 21:00.880
Even though we only came in second place

21:00.880 --> 21:02.270
in the junior high regional finals,

21:02.270 --> 21:03.830
didn't Jiang still let us
get special admission

21:03.830 --> 21:05.230
to Hongjing No. 8 High School?

21:05.230 --> 21:07.260
Back then,
we were all in one talent class.

21:07.260 --> 21:08.500
That was great.

21:08.520 --> 21:09.280
So what?

21:10.590 --> 21:12.270
Didn't he abandon us in the end?

21:12.270 --> 21:12.880
Exactly.

21:13.270 --> 21:14.030
When the talent class was disbanded,

21:14.030 --> 21:15.750
did anyone ask for our opinion?

21:15.750 --> 21:17.350
We made a fuss
at the Academic Affairs Office with Qin,

21:17.350 --> 21:19.110
and almost got a demerit, right?

21:19.110 --> 21:21.110
We all ended up as transfer students

21:21.110 --> 21:22.480
and were looked down on wherever we went.

21:22.480 --> 21:23.790
Don't tell me you've all forgotten.

21:23.790 --> 21:25.050
And that Jiang Tianyu.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.590
If he hadn't left,

21:27.000 --> 21:29.800
would we have been disbanded
in our freshman year?

21:34.310 --> 21:36.790
How many orders of
salted egg yolk chicken wings do you want?

21:36.790 --> 21:37.790
Are 2 enough?

21:38.550 --> 21:39.550
That's not enough.

21:39.550 --> 21:40.640
We need at least 4.

21:44.500 --> 21:45.740
You guys order.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.920
I'm telling you.

21:47.920 --> 21:49.240
I want the shredded potatoes.

21:49.240 --> 21:51.750
-I want bullfrog.
-And braised pork.

21:51.750 --> 21:52.240
You're too slow.

21:52.240 --> 21:53.030
Give it to me. Give it to me.

21:53.030 --> 21:54.000
Too slow.

21:54.000 --> 21:54.590
Do you want braised pork?

21:54.590 --> 21:56.550
Yes, two orders.

21:56.550 --> 21:57.790
-Stir-fried beef.
-You guys keep ordering.

21:57.790 --> 21:59.310
Three orders.

21:59.310 --> 22:00.030
Just order 2.

22:00.030 --> 22:02.550
-Duck claws.
-Let's get more. 3 orders.

22:02.550 --> 22:03.590
Spicy soft-shelled turtle.

22:03.590 --> 22:04.510
Yes.

22:05.160 --> 22:06.480
Cabbage...

22:06.480 --> 22:07.680
Since there are so many of us,
get 3 orders.

22:07.680 --> 22:08.940
Sure.

22:11.590 --> 22:13.320
Ms. Lin, what do you want to eat?

22:14.110 --> 22:15.160
Let me see.

22:15.160 --> 22:15.790
Okay.

22:23.750 --> 22:25.160
By the way, Ms. Lin,

22:25.160 --> 22:27.590
we won today all thanks to your
elementary school classmate.

22:27.590 --> 22:29.790
Why didn't you invite him to eat with us?

22:31.400 --> 22:34.060
It was just a chance encounter.
No need for that.

22:34.510 --> 22:35.350
Ms. Lin,

22:35.680 --> 22:37.920
he said he was the former coach of Nanton.

22:37.920 --> 22:39.000
Is that true?

22:39.590 --> 22:40.540
Bro,

22:40.560 --> 22:42.030
if he's the former Nanton coach,

22:42.030 --> 22:43.160
I'm Mbappé.

22:43.160 --> 22:44.030
Then I'm Yamal.

22:45.030 --> 22:46.510
If you don't believe me,
I'll check right now

22:46.510 --> 22:47.960
and expose this liar.

22:47.690 --> 22:48.450
[Winfred Wang] [Nanton Fan Forum]

22:48.550 --> 22:50.890
[Winfred Wang]

22:53.650 --> 22:54.150
[Winfred Wang]

22:54.170 --> 22:55.240
[Winfred Wang] [Nanton Fan Forum]

22:57.200 --> 22:59.440
Oh my. Come on.

23:04.030 --> 23:05.550
Wait. Is it really him?

23:05.550 --> 23:06.680
-What?
-Mr. Win.

23:07.640 --> 23:08.350
Is it really him?

23:08.350 --> 23:10.310
-It's really him.
-It's really him?

23:10.310 --> 23:11.680
-I remember him.
-Is it really him?

23:11.680 --> 23:12.350
Mr. Win.

23:13.440 --> 23:16.440
-Hello, excuse me. The food is here.
-The food is here.

23:18.350 --> 23:20.030
-Who cares which team he coaches?
-It's really him.

23:20.030 --> 23:21.310
I'm hungry anyway.

23:21.310 --> 23:22.270
I'll eat first.

23:22.270 --> 23:23.310
Here, Ms. Lin.

23:24.000 --> 23:24.600
Thank you.

23:26.790 --> 23:27.590
By the way, Fu,

23:28.030 --> 23:29.400
the thing you mentioned before—

23:29.400 --> 23:30.790
the weird thing you received—

23:30.790 --> 23:32.590
should you tell me what it is now?

23:40.640 --> 23:41.640
There's nothing.

23:45.690 --> 23:46.540
What?

23:51.930 --> 23:52.930
There's nothing.

23:53.230 --> 23:54.930
I didn't receive anything.

23:56.290 --> 23:57.680
I lied.

24:09.240 --> 24:11.690
I just wanted us
to play football together.

24:27.130 --> 24:28.130
Fu,

24:28.830 --> 24:31.230
you really want to play football
that much?

24:39.880 --> 24:41.170
What was there to look forward to

24:41.170 --> 24:42.830
in a game we were bound to lose?

24:42.860 --> 24:44.790
Was it necessary for you to do this?

24:51.230 --> 24:51.830
It's fine.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.250
Just treat it as a free autumn trip.

24:53.250 --> 24:54.960
And we got a free meal out of it, right?

24:54.960 --> 24:55.880
Yeah, that's right.

24:55.880 --> 24:56.640
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

24:56.640 --> 24:58.720
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.

24:58.720 --> 24:59.920
By the way,

24:59.940 --> 25:01.420
this game is a draw.

25:01.590 --> 25:03.190
Are we going to keep playing?

25:03.680 --> 25:04.590
Keep playing?

25:04.830 --> 25:06.030
Why bother?

25:06.030 --> 25:08.680
They dribbled past us
like we weren't even there.

25:08.680 --> 25:10.670
Have some awareness, bro.

25:10.690 --> 25:12.410
We're just a bunch of losers.

25:12.440 --> 25:14.300
We should just hide in the corner.

25:14.350 --> 25:16.240
Why dream of shining?

25:27.920 --> 25:28.960
Anyway,

25:28.960 --> 25:31.590
we accomplished our mission honorably.

25:31.610 --> 25:33.460
It's good to quit while we're ahead,

25:33.460 --> 25:34.300
isn't it?

25:34.320 --> 25:36.560
Yeah, we don't even have a full team.

25:37.480 --> 25:38.040
Come on.

25:39.270 --> 25:40.920
To our honorable retirement.

25:40.920 --> 25:42.440
-Come on.
-Cheers to losers.

25:42.440 --> 25:43.020
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

25:43.020 --> 25:43.750
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

25:43.750 --> 25:45.110
Cheers!

25:45.110 --> 25:46.350
Cheers!

25:53.400 --> 25:54.920
This is really delicious.

25:54.920 --> 25:55.790
It's really delicious.

25:55.790 --> 25:56.880
You eat this.

25:56.880 --> 25:57.880
I want to eat that.

25:58.160 --> 25:59.160
I want to eat this.

25:59.160 --> 26:00.550
This one is a bit salty.

26:01.590 --> 26:03.650
-This is quite good.
-This is not bad.

26:05.070 --> 26:05.880
I'm so full.

26:05.880 --> 26:07.160
Really stuffed.

26:08.270 --> 26:10.510
Thank you, Ms. Lin,
for treating us to this meal.

26:10.510 --> 26:11.880
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

26:20.610 --> 26:21.670
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

26:21.910 --> 26:22.840
You're welcome.

26:24.270 --> 26:26.330
Do you really like playing football?

26:28.550 --> 26:31.020
Then why don't you look happy?

26:31.040 --> 26:32.990
Isn't today's result quite good?

26:35.030 --> 26:36.110
I am happy.

26:37.150 --> 26:38.350
Just too happy.

26:41.350 --> 26:42.770
Originally, I thought

26:42.800 --> 26:44.460
we'd play one more game with them,

26:44.460 --> 26:46.060
just to satisfy our craving,

26:46.230 --> 26:48.160
since we were bound to lose anyway.

26:48.750 --> 26:50.790
I really thought it was the last game.

26:50.790 --> 26:52.720
If we lost, everyone would give up.

26:54.680 --> 26:55.590
But...

26:57.000 --> 26:58.200
You want to continue?

27:02.720 --> 27:03.510
Ms. Lin, do you think I'm

27:03.510 --> 27:05.240
biting off more than I can chew?

27:05.920 --> 27:06.880
How could I?

27:07.920 --> 27:09.310
If you were really that bad at football,

27:09.310 --> 27:10.720
you wouldn't have been admitted

27:10.720 --> 27:12.310
as sports recruits.

27:13.920 --> 27:15.980
The talent class has been disbanded.

27:16.020 --> 27:18.220
What kind of sports recruits are we now?

27:21.800 --> 27:23.280
Actually, today,

27:23.750 --> 27:25.130
drawing with them

27:25.160 --> 27:26.810
really feels like a dream.

27:32.030 --> 27:33.550
I really love football.

27:36.400 --> 27:37.880
So I don't want it to end.

27:39.350 --> 27:41.350
I know better than anyone else

27:42.400 --> 27:44.330
that we are already in high school.

27:44.830 --> 27:47.830
Those who have what it takes
would have shown it by now.

27:48.160 --> 27:50.000
Football is a game of 11 players.

27:51.070 --> 27:52.400
It's impossible for everyone to be willing

27:52.400 --> 27:54.130
to play along with me like this.

27:57.400 --> 27:58.160
But I...

27:58.830 --> 28:00.760
just can't bring myself to give up.

28:04.240 --> 28:05.070
Ms. Lin,

28:06.740 --> 28:07.910
in this life,

28:08.570 --> 28:10.460
I don't have any chances left.

28:15.350 --> 28:17.550
Fu, stop chatting!

28:17.550 --> 28:20.720
-The bus is here! Let's go!
-Let's go, Fu!

28:20.720 --> 28:21.550
Coming.

28:23.330 --> 28:24.800
Go, go, go!

28:25.400 --> 28:26.790
Hurry up.

28:27.270 --> 28:28.240
Coming!

28:56.000 --> 28:57.680
Why did he go to sleep so early?

28:59.380 --> 29:00.910
I'll thank him another day.

29:27.430 --> 29:28.370
Dream?

29:29.200 --> 29:30.550
I really love football.

29:33.810 --> 29:35.160
So I don't want it to end.

29:37.440 --> 29:39.240
What does that have to do with me?

29:54.200 --> 29:55.640
I knew it.

29:56.720 --> 29:57.890
Wang Fa?

30:04.160 --> 30:04.920
Wang Fa.

30:14.920 --> 30:15.980
Sorry.

30:16.010 --> 30:18.610
I saw your door was unlocked,
so I let myself in.

30:19.670 --> 30:21.020
Miss Landlady,

30:21.040 --> 30:21.880
it's so late.

30:22.640 --> 30:24.240
Is there something you need?

30:26.200 --> 30:27.800
Your floor is leaking water.

30:29.750 --> 30:30.480
Sorry,

30:30.720 --> 30:31.650
I didn't notice.

30:32.480 --> 30:33.310
It's okay,

30:33.310 --> 30:36.030
but please get someone
to fix it as soon as possible.

30:36.030 --> 30:37.430
I didn't scare you, did I?

30:41.870 --> 30:42.910
No.

30:43.330 --> 30:44.840
Holding your breath underwater

30:44.840 --> 30:46.880
must be for seeking inner peace.

30:47.480 --> 30:48.400
I suggest you

30:48.400 --> 30:50.600
try diving. The effect might be better.

30:51.230 --> 30:52.650
It seems you

30:52.830 --> 30:54.930
know a lot about psychology.

30:54.960 --> 30:56.690
It's just a friendly reminder.

30:56.880 --> 30:58.220
After all, I am your landlady.

30:58.220 --> 30:59.920
If anything really happens to you,

30:59.920 --> 31:01.520
it will be very tricky for me.

31:17.620 --> 31:19.630
[Administrative Building]

31:38.880 --> 31:39.740
Director Qian,

31:40.070 --> 31:41.330
I've thought about it.

31:41.830 --> 31:43.870
The football team's draw this time

31:43.900 --> 31:45.960
shows they're actually pretty good.

31:46.000 --> 31:48.800
What they need
is a more professional supervisor.

31:51.170 --> 31:52.370
I think...

31:53.880 --> 31:56.180
the teachers in the P.E. department
are very suitable.

31:56.180 --> 31:57.040
Director,

31:57.070 --> 31:58.010
I can't do it.

32:01.270 --> 32:02.590
Ms. Lin,

32:02.610 --> 32:05.510
the fact that you achieved such a result
the first time you led the team

32:05.510 --> 32:07.830
means you are very competent

32:07.850 --> 32:09.880
-for the position of supervisor.
-Here we go ahain.

32:09.880 --> 32:11.350
You must continue
to work hard in the future.

32:11.350 --> 32:13.790
Director, I really can't do it.

32:15.310 --> 32:16.310
Actually, in the P.E. department,

32:16.310 --> 32:18.260
the other teachers' schedules
are very full.

32:18.260 --> 32:20.110
Mr. Li, that track and field competition
of yours,

32:20.110 --> 32:21.550
is it going to start soon?

32:21.550 --> 32:23.550
Yes, our track and field team
is very busy with training.

32:23.550 --> 32:25.110
The competition will start next month.

32:25.110 --> 32:26.350
Your ball game competition...

32:26.350 --> 32:28.000
Our basketball group
also has a competition next month.

32:28.000 --> 32:29.350
Ball games group is also very busy.

32:29.350 --> 32:30.030
I can't do it.

32:30.030 --> 32:31.290
I don't know anything.

32:31.440 --> 32:32.110
Look at them.

32:32.110 --> 32:33.940
All of them are actually very busy.

32:33.940 --> 32:34.780
Alright,

32:35.110 --> 32:36.510
we are back to square one.

32:38.350 --> 32:39.350
Ms. Lin,

32:39.920 --> 32:41.480
you haven't been at the school for long.

32:41.480 --> 32:43.790
I have to tell you
the truth about some things.

32:43.790 --> 32:45.440
Actually, the competition
for positions in the school

32:45.440 --> 32:47.110
is very fierce.

32:47.830 --> 32:49.590
-He's going to use his trump card again.
-Especially during the probation period.

32:49.590 --> 32:51.680
It mainly depends on your performance.

32:51.680 --> 32:52.920
You see, you are a contract worker,

32:52.920 --> 32:54.550
and you haven't become
a regular employee yet, right?

32:54.550 --> 32:56.550
How can you become
a regular employee then?

32:56.550 --> 32:57.720
You have to complete...

32:57.720 --> 33:00.590
-I was too naive.
-the task assigned by the school leaders

33:00.590 --> 33:01.510
and achieve good results.

33:01.510 --> 33:03.480
I actually believed
that it was just a one-round tour,

33:03.480 --> 33:05.030
just going through the motions.

33:05.030 --> 33:08.550
Now it seems that I have to
take this job whether I want to or not.

33:08.550 --> 33:10.050
That's impossible.

33:10.550 --> 33:12.400
So what counts as achieving good results?

33:12.400 --> 33:13.550
I think

33:13.550 --> 33:16.110
you have to make it out of the preliminaries
and into the next round.

33:16.110 --> 33:17.030
The next round?

33:19.000 --> 33:20.070
But...

33:20.720 --> 33:22.320
they don't even have a coach.

33:22.400 --> 33:23.350
Ms. Lin,

33:23.920 --> 33:25.380
you are absolutely right.

33:25.590 --> 33:27.030
As the team supervisor,

33:27.030 --> 33:28.790
you have the responsibility and obligation

33:28.790 --> 33:31.110
to find a coach for the team.

33:31.110 --> 33:31.790
Me? Find a coach?

33:31.790 --> 33:33.720
Hurry up and do it now.

33:35.510 --> 33:36.550
Ms. Lin,

33:36.920 --> 33:39.880
completing the task assigned to you
by the school leadership

33:39.880 --> 33:41.680
is a very honorable thing.

33:41.680 --> 33:44.050
Where am I supposed to find a coach?

33:44.080 --> 33:45.080
Go for it.

33:50.360 --> 33:51.320
Go for it.

33:56.070 --> 33:56.830
Director Qian,

33:56.830 --> 33:57.830
school is over, so I'm leaving now.

33:57.830 --> 33:58.590
-Okay.
-Okay.

33:58.590 --> 33:59.510
Bye.

34:01.830 --> 34:03.070
Goodbye, Ms. Lin.

34:08.929 --> 34:10.820
This is too hard for me.

34:12.550 --> 34:15.699
[The Second General Assembly
of the Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team]

34:12.590 --> 34:14.360
The second general sssembly...

34:14.360 --> 34:16.000
I'm melting, bro.

34:16.000 --> 34:17.480
I can't stand it anymore.

34:17.480 --> 34:18.480
What are we doing?

34:18.800 --> 34:19.590
Let's go.

34:22.190 --> 34:23.449
-It stinks.
-Seriously.

34:23.449 --> 34:25.530
-Why did she call us here?
-Who knows?

34:26.760 --> 34:27.620
Hello, Ms. Lin.

34:30.860 --> 34:32.130
Alright, babies.

34:32.159 --> 34:32.850
Sit down.

34:34.150 --> 34:35.679
I'm not a baby.

34:36.400 --> 34:37.920
What kind of baby eats 3 meals a day,

34:37.920 --> 34:39.630
and 5 bowls of rice per meal?

34:42.139 --> 34:44.620
Ms. Lin, please watch your words.

34:46.620 --> 34:47.530
Got it.

34:47.560 --> 34:49.040
My dear ba-

34:49.150 --> 34:51.780
-ttle-tested students.

34:52.110 --> 34:53.050
Find a place to sit.

34:53.050 --> 34:54.050
You are not a baby.

34:54.070 --> 34:55.510
-Sit.
-Baby Lin Lu, let's go.

34:55.139 --> 34:57.370
[The Second General Assembly
of the Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team]

35:00.920 --> 35:01.670
You should know

35:01.670 --> 35:03.510
why I called you here, right?

35:04.510 --> 35:05.400
We refuse.

35:07.440 --> 35:08.230
That fast?

35:09.280 --> 35:10.190
Won't you...

35:10.550 --> 35:11.590
consider it?

35:11.590 --> 35:13.150
What's there to consider?

35:13.150 --> 35:15.410
In the school's eyes,
we're just a bunch of hooligans.

35:15.410 --> 35:17.120
The school doesn't value
our football team at all.

35:17.120 --> 35:18.040
Why waste time?

35:18.480 --> 35:20.360
A-Actually, it's really rare for us

35:20.360 --> 35:21.390
to have this opportunity.

35:21.390 --> 35:22.970
There's nothing wrong
with continuing to play,

35:22.970 --> 35:23.940
is there?

35:24.230 --> 35:24.920
Right?

35:29.150 --> 35:30.920
Fine, let's give it a try.

35:31.440 --> 35:33.400
What if they abandon us again

35:33.400 --> 35:34.730
after a couple of games?

35:34.960 --> 35:36.230
This time, the school

35:36.230 --> 35:38.150
really wants to rebuild the team

35:38.150 --> 35:40.670
and win back the title
of Football Characteristic Campus.

35:40.670 --> 35:42.710
That's a bit too ambitious.

35:43.030 --> 35:44.110
Yeah, Ms. Lin.

35:44.110 --> 35:45.110
We were just lucky last time

35:45.110 --> 35:46.680
to tie with Ning'an Experimental School.

35:46.680 --> 35:48.230
And the school wants us to rebuild the

35:48.230 --> 35:49.670
Football Characteristic Campus?

35:49.670 --> 35:51.030
I think this task

35:51.110 --> 35:52.200
is too heavy for us.

35:52.220 --> 35:54.070
Besides, we don't even have a coach.

35:54.070 --> 35:56.400
We are trying hard to find a coach
already.

35:56.480 --> 35:57.440
Ms. Lin.

35:57.880 --> 35:58.830
I'm wondering,

35:58.860 --> 35:59.760
is it possible for us

35:59.760 --> 36:01.760
to hire a top-level coach?

36:02.440 --> 36:04.700
Like your elementary school classmate.

36:04.800 --> 36:05.760
-Yeah.
-Yes.

36:05.760 --> 36:07.020
I think that will work.

36:07.190 --> 36:08.880
With a former Nanton coach leading us,

36:08.880 --> 36:11.010
our team would actually have a chance.

36:11.440 --> 36:13.100
He's really got some skills.

36:13.400 --> 36:14.230
But...

36:14.800 --> 36:16.590
can we actually invite him over?

36:16.590 --> 36:18.550
That's Nanton, bro.

36:18.550 --> 36:19.710
How is that possible?

36:19.710 --> 36:21.110
Is it really impossible?

36:21.590 --> 36:23.590
Maybe Ms. Lin isn't capable enough.

36:29.070 --> 36:30.170
I'll try my best.

36:31.030 --> 36:31.960
Alright.

36:31.960 --> 36:33.600
If you can get him to come,

36:34.110 --> 36:34.800
we'll play.

36:40.510 --> 36:41.240
For real?

36:41.260 --> 36:42.490
For real.

36:42.980 --> 36:43.900
Really.

36:46.280 --> 36:47.230
Alright.

36:47.280 --> 36:48.470
I'll try.

37:18.740 --> 37:19.670
Wen Chengye,

37:19.840 --> 37:21.160
why did you trick me?

37:21.330 --> 37:22.730
Let me teach you a lesson.

37:22.960 --> 37:25.090
Don't easily trust others' promises.

37:25.590 --> 37:27.440
You seem very hostile towards me.

37:27.440 --> 37:29.110
I have never offended you, right?

37:29.110 --> 37:29.760
Is that so?

37:33.100 --> 37:33.900
Think again.

37:38.110 --> 37:39.030
Wen Chengye.

37:40.680 --> 37:42.480
Lay a finger on Fu and you'll see.

37:45.540 --> 37:47.200
Seems you've got a new friend.

37:48.590 --> 37:49.440
An idiot.

37:49.440 --> 37:50.510
Who are you calling an idiot?

37:50.510 --> 37:51.970
We just drew with Ning'an.

37:53.670 --> 37:54.870
What's with the "oh"?

37:55.380 --> 37:57.410
What does it matter to me?

37:58.000 --> 37:58.960
Idiots.

38:00.110 --> 38:01.320
A bunch of idiots.

38:01.320 --> 38:02.340
Say that again.

38:02.520 --> 38:03.650
-Come back!
-Qin Ao!

38:18.780 --> 38:21.010
[Director Qian]

38:21.390 --> 38:22.460
Ms. Lin,

38:22.480 --> 38:23.850
did you find a coach?

38:23.910 --> 38:25.840
The principal gave the order.

38:25.840 --> 38:28.670
You must find a way to form the team

38:28.670 --> 38:30.880
and achieve some results.

38:30.900 --> 38:33.090
Good luck. I believe in you.

38:42.740 --> 38:44.570
Asking him shouldn't require money, right?

38:43.060 --> 38:43.580
[Director Qian]

38:43.700 --> 38:45.240
[Contacts]

38:45.340 --> 38:46.970
[New Friends] [I'm Winfred]

38:47.060 --> 38:47.260
[Please wait]

38:47.380 --> 38:49.170
[Permission Settings]

38:49.170 --> 38:50.070
[Processing]

38:57.940 --> 38:59.010
[Slack Superstar]

39:06.190 --> 39:07.620
Mr. Win,

39:07.640 --> 39:09.320
I would like to take the liberty to ask,

39:09.320 --> 39:12.220
shouldn't the water leak problem
be solved?

39:15.300 --> 39:16.410
I found someone.

39:16.440 --> 39:18.370
They will start working tomorrow.

39:22.670 --> 39:24.670
By the way, I have another question.

39:24.720 --> 39:26.320
Would you be willing...

39:26.340 --> 39:28.330
to coach those kids from last time?

39:43.510 --> 39:44.400
No.

39:47.270 --> 39:49.070
I knew it.

39:49.190 --> 39:49.840
No way.

39:50.510 --> 39:51.590
For Grandpa,

39:51.610 --> 39:53.020
I must keep this job.

39:56.840 --> 39:58.110
What should I do?

40:08.570 --> 40:10.250
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

40:11.190 --> 40:12.680
♪ Because you're with me ♪

40:15.420 --> 40:16.950
♪ The light shimmers ♪

40:18.210 --> 40:19.540
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

40:20.970 --> 40:22.290
♪ Running towards you ♪

40:23.080 --> 40:24.590
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

40:28.140 --> 40:29.300
♪ Walk side by side ♪

40:30.690 --> 40:32.880
♪ Become ourselves ♪
